From 30e6a08a7c4706c7006610fc458d0c4b6ba2ba9b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Johannes Berg <johannes.berg@intel.com>
Date: Sat, 10 May 2025 21:48:18 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: iwlwifi: cfg: fix and unify Killer/JF configs
Git-commit: 30e6a08a7c4706c7006610fc458d0c4b6ba2ba9b
Patch-mainline: v6.16-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

All of these should be 160 MHz, and they can be recognised
by just the subdevice ID. Unify all the Killer/JF entries.

Signed-off-by: Johannes Berg <johannes.berg@intel.com>
Signed-off-by: Miri Korenblit <miriam.rachel.korenblit@intel.com>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20250510214621.a93788f159ec.I114f09a0f61849ac3b75d12d7def35be842e5b7c@changeid
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
